.name
WorldTime
.author
Jonathan Potter 
.version
1.31
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A clock that has two states.  In the first state, it has a small window
which shows the current time and also the current time in another city in
the world.  In the second state, a large window shows the time in 84 cities
throughout the world.  The list of cities is configurable.  
